"                                                                           Vim:


"                                  Composition:

diw  " delete word under cursor
ggVG " select the whole file
ca'  " delete the text in single quote under the cursor (quotes included) and
     " enters insert mode
de   " deletes until the end of the word under the cursor
ci)  " deletes the content of the closer () block under the cursor and enters
     " insert mode
